snippet.title: Containment Zone Teaser #1 (Coming Soon)
snippet.description:
Containment Zone is a game I have been working on in Unity Game Engine for a while now and will soon be released to steam.
This is the first teaser of many for the game(Still a work in progress)
This will be my first steam release game when it is complete.
